{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-chapter-level-1-chapter-level-1-tsx","path":"/topics/sepsis/supporting-evidence/","result":{"pageContext":{"chapter":{"id":"c0cc5534-3a65-5215-b06f-82d0952f8728","slug":"supporting-evidence","fullItemName":"Supporting evidence","depth":1,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field 60bbe132-0aaf-448c-a626-aa0600a5693f --><h1>Supporting evidence</h1><!-- end field 60bbe132-0aaf-448c-a626-aa0600a5693f -->","summary":null,"htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item 7a178eac-7b94-4b50-9019-aa0600a5693f --><!-- begin field 1a8dcfe0-ff03-4164-8bf7-aa0600a5693f --><p>This CKS topic is largely based on the National Institute for Health and Care Excellence (NICE) clinical guidelines <em>Sepsis: recognition, assessment and early management</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/sepsis/references/\">NICE, 2019</a>] and <em>Neutropenic sepsis: prevention and management in people with cancer</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/sepsis/references/\">NICE, 2012</a>], the international consensus report <em>Surviving Sepsis Campaign (SSC): International Guidelines for Management of Sepsis and Septic Shock: 2016</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/sepsis/references/\">Rhodes, 2017</a>], a consensus document published by a Task Force of the Society of Critical Care Medicine and the European Society of Intensive Care Medicine <em>The Third International Consensus Definitions for Sepsis and Septic Shock (Sepsis-3)</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/sepsis/references/\">Singer, 2016</a>], the UK Sepsis Trust <em>Sepsis Manual</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/sepsis/references/\">Daniels, 2017</a>], a Royal College of General Practitioners (RCGP) publication <em>Sepsis: guidance for GPs</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/sepsis/references/\">RCGP, 2018</a>], and expert opinion in review articles. The rationale for the individual recommendations is discussed in the relevant basis for recommendation sections.</p><!-- end field 1a8dcfe0-ff03-4164-8bf7-aa0600a5693f --><!-- end item 7a178eac-7b94-4b50-9019-aa0600a5693f -->","topic":{"id":"6934ac75-4c45-5f2f-8c9a-2d8851f1adf5","topicId":"eab5610a-80e3-49d5-ac25-aa0600a5625f","topicName":"Sepsis","slug":"sepsis","lastRevised":"Last revised in April 2020","chapters":[{"id":"21403d5c-7f6a-58f8-a754-f80facfcc7b7","fullItemName":"Summary","slug":"summary","subChapters":[]},{"id":"01bfd22f-a788-595c-9d77-4f15e7d21471","fullItemName":"Have I got the right topic?","slug":"have-i-got-the-right-topic","subChapters":[]},{"id":"8280962c-6cb2-53a1-8eed-ec18c19db62a","fullItemName":"How up-to-date is this topic?","slug":"how-up-to-date-is-this-topic","subChapters":[{"id":"02ea2408-9b6e-5954-a3bc-8305ad7c2b3d","slug":"changes","fullItemName":"Changes"},{"id":"c2a838a7-45f2-5a2b-8e94-13f83b057517","slug":"update","fullItemName":"Update"}]},{"id":"a1a6b520-0d3e-5568-8fcf-e882ce604048","fullItemName":"Goals and outcome measures","slug":"goals-outcome-measures","subChapters":[{"id":"a9d2a1af-b338-5209-93b4-bddc7b6b5cbd","slug":"goals","fullItemName":"Goals"},{"id":"b2606ff0-0e97-55b2-83e3-4b0c5d0a2be2","slug":"outcome-measures","fullItemName":"Outcome measures"},{"id":"3c4a84a7-c8f8-551b-bf15-639adaa8882d","slug":"audit-criteria","fullItemName":"Audit criteria"},{"id":"af6a0131-ac12-5bf9-9ae2-5a74b2adbde7","slug":"qof-indicators","fullItemName":"QOF indicators"},{"id":"379dd412-6848-5408-bbec-b555f59bfc67","slug":"qipp","fullItemName":"QIPP"},{"id":"cae1293c-e888-54e5-a1dd-6f9b76935048","slug":"nice-quality-standards","fullItemName":"NICE quality standards"}]},{"id":"e59cb5ea-715e-5c86-a9eb-1321bb0a362f","fullItemName":"Background information","slug":"background-information","subChapters":[{"id":"6ca10715-009f-5d48-ae98-5f1104993328","slug":"definition","fullI